Port number for IRC: 6667 (sometimes 6668, 6669)

IRCs have a bunch of channels - choose the one you want to join

Register your nickname first

/msg NickServ REGISTER <password> <email address>

Identify yourself every time you join a channel

/msg NickServ IDENTIFY <password>

CAREFUL WITH THE ABOVE!!!

To join Offensive Security:

/join #offsec

To PM (private message/IM) someone:

/msg <nickname> <message>
